            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">1. 15 year old boy comes to the office because of occasional shortness of breath every few weeks. Currently he feels well. he uses no medication and denies any other medical problems.hos vitals stable and chest examination is normal.<br />\nWhich of the following is single most diagnostic test at this time?</p>"
